1
00:00:00,320 --> 00:00:02,320
My brother is quite the popular guy.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:04,640
As his older brother,

3
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:07,360
it makes me happy to see him so well-liked.

4
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:21,400
Hey!

5
00:00:22,080 --> 00:00:23,440
Why have you been avoiding eye contact today?

6
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:25,720
I didn't want to bother you.

7
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:28,520
- It's just eye contact.
- How could that possibly be a bother?

8
00:00:32,440 --> 00:00:33,440
Iijima Hinata.

9
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:37,160
- You get along with everyone.
- It's impressive.

10
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:40,040
What's so impressive about that?

11
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:44,000
It's not like I have many friends.

12
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,200
I've known that for a long time.

13
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:51,760
Hey!

14
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:55,520
Are you jealous of my popularity?

15
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:56,880
Not at all.

16
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,480
- Right?
- That's it, isn't it?

17
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,200
You're so cute.

18
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,400
Hey, cut it out.

19
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:05,560
That smug look on your face...

20
00:01:09,160 --> 00:01:10,360
Deep down,

21
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,760
he's just pushing himself too hard.
